<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, July 2 (Xinhua) -- At least 18 people were killed
and 80 injured in an accident in mountainous northern Pakistan
when an overloaded speedy bus fell into a ditch, reports reaching
here said.
</P>
<P>
