Manshera, a major town in Pakistan's North West Frontier Province,
the reports said.
</P>
<P>
The bus was carrying about 120 people, most of them were school
children and laborers who were on their way to schools and working
sites, the reports said.
</P>
<P>
Further details are still awaited. 
