<HEADLINE> President Jiang Zemin Leaves Hong Kong </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 2 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
left here by special plane Thursday after attending the
celebrations of the first anniversary of Hong Kong's return to
