<HEADLINE> URGENT: President Jiang Inspects PLA Troops in HK </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 2 (Xinhua) -- Chinese President Jiang Zemin
came to the Stonecutters Island Naval Base here Thursday morning
to inspect the People's Liberation Army (PLA) troops stationed in
the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR) of China.
</P>
<P>
Jiang, who is also general secretary of the Central Committee
of the Communist Party of China and chairman of the Central
Military Committee, will review a guard of honor and elements of
the three services.
</P>
