He will also address officers of the PLA troops. The PLA troops
took over the naval base on July 1, 1997 when China resumed
exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
Jiang came to Hong Kong Tuesday afternoon to take part in
celebrations of the first anniversary of Hong Kong's return to
China and the establishment of the HKSAR. 
