autonomous regions, as well as eight state departments.
</P>
<P>
The fair, which will be held between September 8-12 in the
south China port city of Xiamen, will be jointly sponsored by the
Ministry of Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation (MOFTEC),
Fujian Province and Xiamen.
</P>
